{
  "name": "Spell Scent",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/scout.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Knowledge (arcana) 6 ranks, Perception 6 ranks, Scout sphere (Heightened Awareness, Magehunter&#8217;s Vision).</p>\n<p>After spending three rounds using Heightened Awareness to examine a magic aura, you may track the creature or object that created the magic aura. You gain a circumstance bonus to follow tracks based upon the strength of the examined aura (dim +1, faint +2, moderate +4, strong +8, overwhelming +16). The bonus lasts until you have traveled a number of miles or made a number of Survival checks equal to half your ranks in Perception, or until you use Heightened Awareness to examine another magic aura.</p>\n",
